HEADWORD: Unripe
<hw>Un*ripe"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not ripe;
<as>as, <ex>unripe</ex> fruit</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Developing too early; premature.</def> <rj><au>Sir
